🔥 MVI State Management Guide (MVI.md)

यह डॉक्यूमेंट MVI (Model–View–Intent) pattern में State Management को deep level पर explain करता है — especially Jetpack Compose + Clean Architecture setup के लिए।

---

🧠 MVI क्या है?

MVI =

- Model → State
- View → UI (Compose Screen)
- Intent → User actions

«💡 Core Idea:
UI कभी directly state change नहीं करती।
User → Intent → ViewModel → Reduce → New State → UI»

---

🏗 MVI Flow

User Action
   ↓
Intent
   ↓
ViewModel
   ↓
Reduce (Old State + Intent)
   ↓
New State
   ↓
UI Recompose

---

🎯 MVI क्यों Use करें?

MVVM| MVI
Multiple states| Single immutable state
Mutable updates| Reducer pattern
Hard to debug| Predictable flow
Side effects mix| Controlled side effects

