🏆 Why MVI is Powerful?

✅ Single source of truth
✅ Predictable state transitions
✅ Debug friendly
✅ Easy to log
✅ Great for complex screens
✅ Ideal for fintech / ride apps / trading apps

---

⚠️ Common Mistakes

❌ Multiple StateFlow
❌ Side effects inside state
❌ Direct state mutation
❌ Business logic inside reducer
❌ Huge ViewModel

---

🧠 Golden Rules

- Intent = User action
- Action = Internal event
- State = UI model
- Effect = One-time event
- Reducer = Pure function

---

📊 MVVM vs MVI Comparison

Feature| MVVM| MVI
State| Multiple| Single
Debugging| Medium| Easy
Predictability| Medium| High
Complexity| Simple| Advanced
Enterprise Ready| Yes| Highly

---

🏁 Final Summary

MVI State Management:

- Single immutable state
- Intent driven UI
- Reducer based state updates
- Side effects separated
- Highly scalable
- Best for complex apps
